w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/morrissey-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/morrissey">莫里西</a>声称国会唱片公司的首席执行官正试图破坏他的职业生涯。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/morrissey-at-riot-fest-review-chicago-3048341">莫里西在防暴节评论——流行音乐的问题叔叔明智地闭嘴并播放热门歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位独唱家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯乐队</a>歌手周日（10 月 15 日） <a href="https://www.morrisseycentral.com/messagesfrommorrissey/capitol-wreckers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在他的网站上</a>发布了一张国会唱片公司徽标的图片，标题为“CAPITOL WRECKERS”，但他的攻击没有任何依据。</p><p>他还附上了一张 Capitol Music Group 主席兼首席执行官 Michelle Jubelirer 的照片，并写道：“嗨！我经营国会唱片公司，如果我想毁掉莫里西的事业，没有人能阻止我。再见了！”</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系 Capitol Records 征求意见，但该唱片公司尚未做出回应。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrisseys-new-album-bonfire-of-teenagers-to-feature-miley-cyrus-iggy-pop-flea-and-more-3338982">Capitol Records 于 2022 年秋季与 Morrissey 合作发行了他的专辑《Bonfire Of Teenagers》</a> ，这位歌手称其为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-announces-new-album-bonfire-of-teenagers-the-best-album-of-my-life-2952106">“我一生中最好的专辑”</a> 。到去年 12 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-departs-label-miley-cyrus-taken-off-bonfire-of-teenagers-3371299">莫里西已经与该品牌断绝关系</a>。</p><p>他还透露，曾在 2020 年为“Bonfire…”歌曲“I Am Veronica”录制和声的麦莉·赛勒斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> ) 要求将她的声音从歌曲中删除。</p><p>正如<a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2239185/morrissey-says-capitol-records-ceo-wants-to-wreck-his-career/news/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Stereogum</em></a>指出的那样，《青少年的篝火》仍然是 Capitol 发行的，而莫里西在过去的一年里一直与该厂牌发生公开争执。</p><p>二月份，他宣布他“开始相信”Capitol 正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-is-quickly-coming-around-to-that-belief-that-capitol-is-sabotaging-his-new-album-3394087">“故意破坏”</a>他的专辑。一周后，他说国会大厦正在宣传“萨姆·史密斯的‘撒旦主义’”，但不是他的专辑。</p><p>莫里西关于国会大厦的最新帖子以一段有人驾驶飞机飞越国会大厦办公室的视频结尾，视频后面附有一条信息：“释放莫子的《青少年篝火》！”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/officialmoz?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@officialmoz</a>你如何引起别人的注意？你驾驶飞机飞过他们的大楼！ <a href="https://twitter.com/capitolrecords?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@capitolrecords</a>请释放 Moz 的“青少年篝火”！第三天<a href="https://t.co/LQQCl3hzqL">pic.twitter.com/LQQCl3hzqL</a></p><p> — 特伦斯·斯坦普 (@TerranceStamp) <a href="https://twitter.com/TerranceStamp/status/1713031902607634831?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这位创作型歌手的上一张专辑是 2020 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/morrissey-i-am-not-a-dog-on-a-chain-review-2623817#:~:text=Significant%20parts%20of%20the%20album,indie%20pop%20and%20rapacious%20rockabilly.">I Am Not A Dog On A Chain</a> 》。 Earlier this year he revealed that he&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-has-recorded-a-new-album-called-without-music-the-world-dies-3401844">recorded a new album titled &#39;Without Music The World Dies</a> &#39; and has been appealing for labels or “private investors” to release the record.</p><p> Meanwhile, Morrissey announced recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-announces-2023-tour-dates-in-asia-and-australia-3479470">new 2023 tour dates in Asia and Australia</a> – see the full list of dates <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-announces-2023-tour-dates-in-asia-and-australia-3479470">here</a> . The singer wrapped a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-summer-2023-uk-ireland-tour-tickets-3425160">UK and Ireland headline tour</a> this summer.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-claims-capitol-records-boss-wants-to-wreck-his-career-3516249">Morrissey claims Capitol Records boss wants to “wreck” his career</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">